2. **Recall**: All visible crawler cranes in the image are localized by a bounding box. There are no additional crawler cranes that are left unannotated.
3. **Fit**: The bounding boxes are neither too loose nor too tight. They enclose the cranes appropriately without cutting off significant parts of the cranes or including too much of the surrounding area.
